tafsir[227]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"(Taa, Siin, Miim) hari yewtanooma fii yeru majje ka fu…ó…óoode Simoore Albaqara."
  26,2,"∆äen ko Aayeeje Alqur'aanaare …ìannginde seerndunde hakkunde Goonga kan e meere nden."
  26,3,"Belajo'o -an Nulaa…óo- sabu rer…óugol maa…óa fii fewnugol …ìe a waray wonkii maa…óa kin sabu suno e rer…óugol fii fewnugol …ìe."
  26,4,"Si Men Muuyii jippinngol Maande e ma…ì…ìe immorde ka kammu Men jippinay nde e ma…ì…ìe, daa…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen √±alla yankinanaade nde hara ko …óe hoyu…óe, kono Men Muuyaali …óum ka ndarndagol …ìe: Mbela…ìe gom…óinay ko wirnii kon?"
  26,5,"Arataa e …ìee sirkoo…ìe immorde e waaju fu…ó…óaa- ngu jippineede immorde ka Hinnorante On e Hujjaaji maggu tinndin…ói …óin fii Ngootimmbaaku Makko e Goongugol Annabaajo Makko on si wanaa …ìe …óuuroto gaayi jentagol mo e goongin- gol mo."
  26,6,"Gom…óii …ìe fennii ko Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen addani …ìe kon, aroyay e ma…ì…ìe goonginal kumpital ko …ìe wonunoo jalkitude kon, Lepte …óen jippoo e ma…ì…ìe."
  26,7,"∆Åee luttay e deppitagol e dow keefeeru ma…ì…ìe hara …ìe ndaaraali faade e leydi ndin no foti hewde ko Men fu…óini e mayri immorde e kala noone e nooneeji pu…ói fotu…ói ndaarugol …óuu…óu…ói nafoore?!"
  26,8,"Pellet, wonii e fu…óinngol ka leydi pu…ói luutondir…ói nooneeji daliili …ìanngu…óo fii Hattannde On fu…óin…óo …ói e dow wurnitugol may…ìe …ìen, …ìur…ìe …ìen e ma…ì…ìe wonaali gom…óin…ìe."
  26,9,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo- ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo go…ó…óo foolataa Mo, ko O Yurmetee…óo jeyaa…ìe makko …ìen."
  26,10,"Ja≈ãto -an Nulaa…óo- tuma nde Joomi maa…óa noddunoo Muusaa ko O Yamir…óo mo yo o aru ka yim…ìe too√±ir…ìe …ìen yeddugol ma…ì…ìe Alla e maccin…óinngol yim…ìe Muusaa …ìen."
  26,11,"∆Åen ko yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen, yo o yamir …ìe e hoore no newori kulol Alla e …óoftaade Yamiraa…ói Makko …óin e wo…ó…óitaade ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin."
  26,12,"Muusaa (yo o his) maaki: ""Min dey, mi…óo huli wata …ìe fennan e nder ko mi yottinta e ma…ì…ìe kon Nulal maa…óa ngal"""
  26,13,"∆Åernde am nden …ìittoo sabu ko …ìe fennatan mi kon, …óemngal am ngal soko fii wowlugol, awa Nulu Jibriila (yo o his) faade e kotoo am Haaruuna fii yo o wonu walloowo lam."
  26,14,"No wonani …ìe e dow am bakkaatu sabu warugol qibtiyankoojo, mi…óo huli wata …ìe warto lam."
  26,15,"Alla Daalani Muusaa (yo o his): ""wanaa non, …ìe warataa ma, yaadu e kotoo maa…óa Haaruuna wonndude e Aayeeje Amen tinndin…óe …óen e goongugol moo…óon. Pellet, Menen Me…óen wonndiri e moo…óo ballal ngal e semmbinngol ngol ko Men jentii…ìe ko wowloton kon e ko wowlante …óon kon, hay e huunde e …óum fuutotaako Men."
  26,16,"Aree ka Fir'awna, wi'anon mo: ""Menen …óoo …ói…óo ko men Nulaa…ìe e maa…óa immorde ka Jooma tageefooji …óin fow."""
  26,17,"Fii yo a accitu …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen …ìen, wonndude e amen."
  26,18,"Fir'awna wi'ani Muusaa (yo o his): ""Enee, men ne'aano ma ka amen …óoo hari ko o penuujo, √±ii…ìu…óaa hakkunde duu…ìi e ngurndam maa…óam, ko hommbo yamirmaa nodditagol Annabaaku?"""
  26,19,"Gollu…óaa fiyaake maw…óe tuma waruno…óaa qibtiyankoojo on fii jinngngol gorko jeyaa…óo ka yim…ìe maa…óa, an ko a yeyaa…óo e yeddu…ìe neemaaji am …óin e dow maa…óa."
  26,20,"Muusaa (yo o his) maakani Fir'awna: ""Mi warii on gorko hari min ko e majju…ìe …ìen mi jeyaa ado Wahayu arude e am."""
  26,21,"Mi doguno on …ìaawo warugol mo, mi yahi ka saare Madyana, nde mi hulunoo wata on warto lam fii makko, Joomi am okkin mi ganndal, O wa…óin mi jeyaa…óo e Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen …ìe O Nulata …óum faade e yim…ìe …ìen."
  26,22,"Ko ne'u…óaa mi kon a maccin…óinaali lam wonndude e maccin…óinngol maa…óa …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen …óum ko neema mo wajitirtaa mi …óum e goonga, kono …óum ha…óataa lam e noddugol ma [ka Diina]."
  26,23,"Fir'awna wi'ani Muusaa (yo o his): ""Ko hommbo jeyi tageefooji …óin, on mo aa∆¥oto…óaa wonndema an ko a Nulaa…óo makko?!"""
  26,24,"Muusaa jaabii Fir'awna o maaki: ""Jooma tageefooji …óin ko Kanko woni Jooma kammuuli …óin e Jooma leydi ndin, e Jooma ko woni kon hakkunde majji. Si tawii on laatike ko on yananaa…ìe wonnde pellet, ko Kanko woni Jooma majji haray rewee Mo Kanko tun."
  26,25,"Fir'awna wi'ani …ìen wonu…ìe fee makko immorde e koohoo…ìe …ìen ka yim…ìe makko: ""Enee, on jentotaako jaabawol Muusaa ngol, e ko woni kon e makko immorde e aa∆¥agol fenaande?!"""
  26,26,"Muusaa maakani …ìe (yo o his): "" Ko Alla woni Joomi moo…óon e Jooma baabiraa…ìe moo…óon adinoo…ìe …ìen."""
  26,27,"Fir'awna wi'i: ""Pellet, on aa∆¥ii…óo wonnde ko o Nulaa…óo faade e moo…óon ko o feetu…óo, o anndaa ko honno o jaaborta, himo wowla kadi ko hakkile ja…ìataa."""
  26,28,"Muusaa maaki: ""On Alla Mo mi noddata on faade e Muu…óum, ko Kanko woni Jooma funnaange e hirnaange, e Jooma ko woni kon hakkunde majji si tawii no laatanii on hakkillaaji …ói hakkilirton …óum""."
  26,29,"Fir'awna wi'ani Muusaa …ìaawo ronkugol makko hujjondirgol e makko: ""Mi woondii si a rewii rewetee…óo tanaa am, mami wa…ói jeyaa…óo e sokaa…ìe …ìen."""
  26,30,"Muusaa (yo o his) maakani Fir'awna: ""A wa…óay lam jeyaa…óo sokaa…ìe …ìen, hay si mi addanii ma ko …ìannginta goongugol am e ko mi addan maa kon immorde ka Alla?"""
  26,31,"O wi'i: ""Addu ko ja≈ãti…óaa kon wonnde no tinndini e goongugol maa…óa si a laatike ko e goongu…ìe …ìen jeya…óaa, e nder kon ko nodditi…óaa …óum""."
  26,32,"Muusaa werlii tuggordu makko ndun ka leydi, e juhayee, ndu waylii biidaane …ìanngu…óo wonannde yi'oo…ìe …ìen."
  26,33,"O naadi junngo makko ngon ka jiiba makko tawi ngo wonaa ranewo, o yaltini ngo ko ngo ranewo, ndaneeri jalbeendi wanaa ndaneeri cul…óugol, ndaaroo…ìe …ìen no seedora ngo non."
  26,34,"Fir'awna wi'ani koohoo…ìe yim…ìe makko, …ìen wonu …ìe ba≈ã≈ãe makko: ""Pellet, oo gorko ko mbileejo anndu…óo mbilewu""."
  26,35,"Himo faandori mbilewu makko ngun yaltinngol on ka leydi moo…óon. Ko hon…óum woni feere moo…óon nde haanu…óen jogaade fii makko?"
  26,36,"∆Åe wi'ani mo: ""Nennan mo nennaa kotoo makko kadi, wata yaccor leptugol …ìe, nulu ka ca'e Misra muu…ìay…ìe mbilee…ìe …ìen""."
  26,37,"Yo…ìe addane kala mbileejo anndu…óo mbilaaku ngun."
  26,38,"Fir'awna moo…ìi mbilee…ìe makko …ìen fii jippirgol e Muusaa e nder nokkuure anndaa nde e jamaanu hettaa…óo."
  26,39,"Yim…ìe …ìen wi'anaa: ""Taw si onon ko on moo…ìotoo…ìe fii yo on yi'u foolu…óo on, e hara ko Muusaa kaa ko mbilee…ìe …ìen?"""
  26,40,"Jortagol wonnde men jokkay mbilee…ìe …ìen ka diina ma…ì…ìe, si tawii ko kam…ìe fooli Muusaa."
  26,41,"Tuma nde mbilee…ìe …ìen arunoo ka Fir'awna fii yo …ìe foolotir e Muusaa …ìe wi'ani mo: ""Yalli no woodani men njo…ìdi jawdi maa…óum teddungal si tawii ko menen fooli Muusaa?"""
  26,42,"Fir'awna wi'ani …ìe: ""Eyyo, njo…ìdi no woodani on, haray si on foolii mo, on wonay …ìa…ótiniraa…ìe ka am jonnugol on darjaaji …ìamtii…ói""."
  26,43,"Muusaa maakani …ìe tawi ko o hoolii…óo Ballal Alla ngal himo …ìanngina wonndema ko o jogii kon wanaa mbilew: ""Li…ìee ko li…ìoton kon immorde e …ìokkoy moo…óon e cawoy moo…óon""."
  26,44,"∆Åe li…ìi …ìokkoy ma…ì…ìe e cawoy ma…ì…ìe koy, …ìe wi'i ka li…ìugol koy: ""Sabu manngu Fir'awna ko menen woni fooloo…ìe …ìen, ko Muusaa woni foolaa…óo on""."
  26,45,"Muusaa li…ìi tuggordu makko ndun, ndu waylii mboddi, tawi kayru hindu mo…óa ko …ìe hul…ìiniray-noo kon yim…ìe …ìen immorde e mbilewu ngun."
  26,46,"Tuma nde mbilee…ìe …ìen yi'unoo tuggordu Muusaa ndun hindu mo…óa ko …ìe li…ìi kon immorde e mbilewu ma…ì…ìe …ìe suuyi …ìe sujji."
  26,47,"∆Åe wi'i: ""Men gom…óinii Jooma tageefooji ndin fow""."
  26,48,"Jooma Muusaa e Haaruuna (yo …ìe his)."
  26,49,"Fir'awna a√±iri mbilee…ìe …ìen gom…óinal ma…ì…ìe ngal, o wi'i: ""Enee, on gom…óinay mo ko adii mi du≈ãanaa- de on …óum?! Pellet, ko Muusaa woni maw…óo moo…óon anndin…óo on on mbilewu ngun. Hari on fow on haldiino fii yaltinngol yim…ìe [saare] Misra nden e nder mayre, kono aray ka anndon ko mi fawata on kon immorde e lepte, mami ta∆¥u sanne koyngal mo kala e junngo makko ngun mi luutindirira hakkunde majje ta∆¥ugol koyngal √±aamal ngal wonndude e junngo nano ngon maa…óum yunnitugol, mami fetu on sanne on fow moo…óon e julle tamaro, mi accataa hay e gooto e moo…óon""."
  26,50,"Mbilee…ìe …ìen wi'ani Fir'awna: ""Tanaa alaa e kon ko kammbirantaa men ta∆¥ugol e fetugol ka aduna, lepte maa…óen iway, menen ko faade ka Joomi amen men ruttotoo, aray O naadoya men ka Yurmeende Makko Duumotoonde."
  26,51,"Menen me…óen jortii nde Alla montanta men goopi amen fe∆¥∆¥u…ói …ói men wa…ó…óitii …óum; sabu men wonii adii…ìe gom…óinnde Muusaa goongina mo."
  26,52,"Men Wahayini e Muusaa Yamirgol mo yo o ro∆¥idu e …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen jemma. Pellet, Fir'awna e wonndu…ìe e makko …ìen …ìe jokkitay …ìe fii yo …ìe artir …ìe."
  26,53,"Fir'awna nuli yoga e konunkee…ìe makko …ìen ka ca'e moo…ìoo…ìe hi…ìe moo…ìa konu ngun fii yo …ìe ruttu …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen nde o anndunoo yaltugol ma…ì…ìe Misra."
  26,54,"Fir'awna wi'i ka fam…óinngol fiyaake …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen: ""Pellet, …ìee ko …ìe fedde fam…óunde""."
  26,55,"Pellet, kam…ìe hi…ìe wa…óude ko men tikkiranta …ìe."
  26,56,"Enen non ko en hebilanii…ìe …ìe, ko en finu…ìe."
  26,57,"Men yaltini Fir'awna e yim…ìe makko …ìen ka leydi Misra joomiraari gese al…óu…óe, e can…ói ilooji ndiyam."
  26,58,"E joomiraare ngaluuji jawdi, e ko…óan…óe mo∆¥∆¥e."
  26,59,"Ko wano Men yaltiniri nii Fir'awna e yim…ìe makko …ìen e …óii neemaaji, Men wa…óani noone …óii neemaaji …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen ka leydi Saami."
  26,60,"Fir'awna e yim…ìe mu'un …ìen yahi e batte [teppe] …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen ka waqtu pu…óal naange."
  26,61,"Tuma nde Fir'awna e yim…ìe mu'un …ìen fewtundirnoo e Muusaa e yim…ìe mu'un, nokku ka wonnoo fedde kala no yi'ude ndeya, yim…ìe Muusaa …ìen wi'i: ""Pellet, Fir'awna e yim…ìe mu'un …ìen …ìe hewtitoto en, en alaa dartantoo…óo en …ìe""."
  26,62,"Muusaa maakani yim…ìe makko …ìen: ""Fiyaake …óen wanaa no miijorton non. Pellet, Joomi am no wonndiri e am semmbinngol e wallugol, O fewnay lam O tinndina lam faade e laawol da…óugol""."
  26,63,"Men Wahayini e Muusaa ko Men yamiray …ìe mo yo o piyir maayo ngon tuggordu makko ndun, o piyiri ngo ndu, maayo ngon seekii ngo wonti boli sappoo e …ói…ói yeru limoore le∆¥∆¥i …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen, kala huntere e ceeki maayo ngon foti e fello mawngo ka tii…óugol e ka tabitugol haa nokku ka ndiyam ilataa e majje."
  26,64,"Men …ìanni Firawna e yim…ìe makko …ìen haa …ìe naati ka maayo ko …ìe sikku…ìe wonnde laawol ngol ko lummbu ngol."
  26,65,"Men danndi Muusaa e …ìen wonndu…ìe e makko immorde e …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen, hay gooto e ma…ì…ìe halkanooka."
  26,66,"Refti Men halkiri Fir'awna e yim…ìe makko …ìen yooleede ka maayo."
  26,67,"Pellet, no e seekanagol maayo ngon Muusaa e da…óugol makko e halkeede Fir'awana e yim…ìe makko …ìen …óum ko Aaya tinndin…óo e dow goongugol Muusaa. ∆Åur…ìe heewude e …ìen wonndunoo…ìe e Fir'awna …ìe wonaano gom…óin…ìe."
  26,68,"Anndu Joomi maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo-ko Kanko woni teddu…óo Yo…ìtotoo…óo ay…ìe Makko …ìen, Yurmetee…óo on tuubu…óo e ma…ì…ìe."
  26,69,"Janngu e taweede ma…ì…ìe -an Nulaa…óo- fillayee fii Ibraahiima."
  26,70,"Tuma nde o wi'annoo baaba makko Aajara e yim…ìe mu'un …ìen: ""Ko hon…óum wonu…óon rewude gaanin Alla?"""
  26,71,"Yim…ìe makko …ìen wi'ani mo: ""Ko sanamuuji men rewata, men √±alla √±ii…ìude e rewugol …ói, ko men jokku…ìe …ói""."
  26,72,"Ibraahiima maakani …ìe: ""Yalli sanamuuji …óin no nana noddaandu mo'on ndun tuma noddoton …ói?"""
  26,73,"Kaa hi…ói nafa on si on …óoftike …ói, maa…óum …ói lorra on si on yeddii …ói?"
  26,74,"∆Åe wi'i: ""∆äi nanantaa men dey si men noddii …ói, …ói nafataa men kadi si men …óoftike …ói, …ói lorrataa men kadi si men yeddii…ói. Ko woni, tigi-tigi on, menen men tawiino baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen hi…ìe gollira nii, me…óen √±entinnde …ìe""."
  26,75,"Ibraahiima maaki: ""Enee, on taskike on yi'ii ko wonu…óon e rewude gaanin Alla immorde e sanamuuji …óin""."
  26,76,"Kon ko baabiraa…ìe moo…óon aran…ìe …ìen laatinoo no rewa."
  26,77,"Pellet, kam…ìe …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe ko …ìe ay…ìe am; sabu kam…ìe ko …ìe meere si wanaa Alla Jooma tageefooji …óin fow."
  26,78,"On Tagu…óo lam ko Kanko fewnata lam faade e mo∆¥∆¥ere aduna e Laakara."
  26,79,"On ko Kanko tun √±amminta lam si mi weelaama, O yarna lam si mi …óon…óaama."
  26,80,"Si mi nawnii ko Kanko tun woni sellinay…óo lam immorde e nawnaare nden, mi alaa sellinoowo ngoo tanaa makko."
  26,81,"E On taw…óo ko Kanko tun warata lam si lajal am ngal timmii, O wurnita lam kadi …ìaawo mayde am nden."
  26,82,"Ko Kanko tun mi jortii yawtanay lam goopi am …óin √ëalnde njo…ìdi ndin."
  26,83,"Ibraahiima noddi Joomi makko o maaki: Joomam okkam faamugol Diina kan, wattidaa mi e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen immorde e Annabaa…ìe adii…ìe lam …ìen, …óum woni naadaa mi ka Aljanna wonndude e ma…ì…ìe""."
  26,84,"Wa…óanaa mi ja≈ãta labaa…óo e mantoore mo∆¥∆¥ere e …óen gire aroyay …óe …ìaawo am."
  26,85,"Wa…óaa lam jeyaa…óo e …ìen ronoo…ìe galleeji Aljanna …óin …ói neemintoo e nder muu…óum jeyaa…ìe Maa…óa gom…óin…ìe …ìen, ho…óinaa lam e nder majji."
  26,86,"Yawtanaa baaba am; kanko o laatinoke jeyaa…óo e majju…ìe …ìen gaay Goonga kan sabu sirku ngun, Ibraahiima du'anii ben makko ko adii …ìanngannde mo wonndema kanko ko o jeyaa…óo e yim…ìe Jahiimi …ìen. Tuma nde …óum …ìanngannoo mo, o danndii mo o du'anaaki mo [hannde kadi]."
  26,87,"Wata A wirtiroyam Lepte …óen √ëalnde yim…ìe …ìen immintinoytee fii hasboore nden."
  26,88,"√ëalnde nde nafataa e muu…óum jawdi ndi ne…ó…óo on faggitii …óum ka aduna makko, wanaa kadi …ìi…ó…ìe …ìe o laatinoo himo wallitora …óum."
  26,89,"Si wanaa on ardu…óo ka Alla e …ìernde hisunde; hara sirku e naafiqaaku alaa e mayre, yiingo e hawtaare alaa e mayre, haray pellet, kanko o nafturay jawdi makko ndi o nafkunoo ndin ka Laawol Alla, e …ìi…ó…ìe makko wonu…ìe du'anaade mo …ìen kadi."
  26,90,"Aljanna on …ìannanee huliroo…ìe Joomi mu'un …ìen …óoftagol Yamiraa…ói Makko …óin, e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin."
  26,91,"Ka Mofturu Yiite ngen fe√±√±inanee majju…ìe …ìen, …ìen majju…ìe gaay Diina Goongaha kan."
  26,92,"∆Åe wi'anee ka ma∆¥inngol …ìe: Honto ko wonuno…óon rewude kon immorde e sanamuuji …óin?"
  26,93,"On reway …ói gaanin Alla? Taw si …ói walliray on ha…óanngol on Lepte Alla …óen, kaa kannji …ói wallay ko'e-majji?"
  26,94,"Wo…ì…ìe e ma…ì…ìe werlee e hoore wo…ì…ìe ka Jahiima e …ìen majjin…ìe …ìe."
  26,95,"E walloo…ìe Ibliisa …ìen immorde e Seytanuuji …óin fow, hay gootil e majji ittintinaaka."
  26,96,"∆Åen sirkoo…ìe wonunoo…ìe rewde tanaa Alla, …ìe jogitii …ìe kafidaa…ìe gaanin Alla, tawi kan…ìe hi…ìe wennjondirde e …ìen rewnoo…ìe …ìe gaanin Alla, …ìe wi'i:"
  26,97,"Men woondirii Alla gom…óii hari men laatike e nder majjere …ìanngunde gaayi Goonga kan."
  26,98,"Tuma nde men fotindirnoo on e Joom tageefooji …óin fow majji, men rewiri on wano men rewirta Mo non."
  26,99,"Majjinaali men gaayi Laawol Goongawol ngol si wanaa …ìen bon…ìe noddu…ìe faade e rewugol …ìe gaanin Alla."
  26,100,"Laatanaaki men tefoo…ìe …ìe no tefanoya men ka Alla fii yo O danndu men immorde e lepte Makko …óen."
  26,101,"Laatanaaki men gi…óo laa…ìu…óo giggol mo no hiwa men o tefanoya men."
  26,102,"Sinndo no woodannoo men artireede ka ngurndam aduna, men wona jeyaa…ìe e gom…óin…ìe Alla …ìen."
  26,103,"Pellet, wonii e koo ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo immorde e fillayee fii Ibraahiima (yo o his), e wa…ótinirde fennu…ìe …ìen tasakuyee, wonannde taskotoo…ìe …ìen, …ìur…ìe heewude e ma…ì…ìe wonaali gom…óin…ìe."
  26,104,"Anndu Joomi maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo- ko Kanko woni teddu…óo Yo…ìtotoo…óo ay…ìe Makko …ìen, Yurmetee…óo on tuubu…óo e ma…ì…ìe."
  26,105,"Yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen fenni Nulaa…ìe …ìen, tuma nde …ìe fennunoo Nuuhu (yo o his)."
  26,106,"Tuma nde Saalihu musi…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on ka dammbe (asko) wi'annoo …ìe: Enee, on hulataa Alla, acciron rewugol tanaa Makko sabu kulol Makko?!"
  26,107,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo moo…óon, Alla Nulii lam e moo…óon, ko mi hoolaa…óo mi …ìeydataa e dow ko Alla Wahayini kon e am, mi uytataa kadi."
  26,108,"Huliree Alla …óoftagol Yamiraa…ói Makko …óin e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaani Makko …óin, …óoftee lam e ko mi yamirta on kon, e ko mi ha…óata on kon e muu…óum."
  26,109,"Mi …óa…ì…ìiraali on njo…ìdi fii ko mi yottinanta Joomi am kon e moo…óon, njo…ìdi am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Alla Jooma tageefooji …óin wanaa e tanaa Makko."
  26,110,"Huliree Alla …óoftagol Yamiraa…ói Makko …óin e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaani Makko …óin, …óoftee lam e ko mi yamirta on kon, e ko mi ha…óata on kon e muu…óum."
  26,111,"Yim…ìe makko …ìen wi'ani mo: Enee, hara men gom…óinte -an Nuuhu- men jokka ko addu…óaa kon men gollira, hara le pellet, jokku…ìe ma …ìen ko e yim…ìe jaasu…ìe …ìen …ìe jeyaako e hoohoo…ìe e teddinaa…ìe …ìen alaa e ma…ì…ìe?!"
  26,112,"Nuuhu maakani …ìe (yo o his): E ko hon…óum woni ganndal am e ko …ìee gom…óin…ìe wonunoo e gollude? Mi laataaki fawtanii…óo …ìe sakko mi mofta golle ma…ì…ìe …óen."
  26,113,"Hasbugol …ìe fawaaki si wanaa Alla, On Anndu…óo gunndooji ma…ì…ìe …óin e fee√±u…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin wanaa ka am, sinndo hi…óon so'aynoo, on wowlataano ko wowlu…óon kon."
