  26,134,"O okki on gese e can…ói ilooji."
  26,135,"Min, mi…óo hulani on -onon yim…ìe am- Lepte √ëalaande mawnde nden ko √ëalnde Darngal."
  26,136,"Yim…ìe makko …ìen wi'ani mo: Ko waajoto…óaa men kon e si a waajaaki no fotana amen ter, men gom…óintaa ma, men ruttataako gaayi ko men woni kon e muu…óum."
  26,137,"…óum wonaali si wanaa diina adinoo…ìe …ìen e naamuuji ma…ì…ìe e jikkuuji ma…ì…ìe."
  26,138,"Men wonaali leptoytee…ìe."
  26,139,"∆Åe jokki yiddugol Annabaajo ma…ì…ìe on Huudu (yo o his), Men halkiri …ìe henndu rimardu ndu sabu fennugol ma…ì…ìe ngol. pellet, wonii e ngol halkugol hangol tasakuyee wonannde taskotoo…ìe …ìen, …ìur…ìe heewude …ìen e ma…ì…ìe wonaali gom…óin…ìe."
  26,140,"Anndu Joomi maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo- ko Kanko woni teddu…óo Yo…ìtotoo…óo ay…ìe Makko …ìen Yurmetee…óo on tuubu…óo immorde e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  26,141,"Samuudinkoo…ìe …ìen finniino Nulaa…ìe …ìen sabu fennugol ma…ì…ìe Annabaajo ma…ì…ìe on Saalihu (yo o his)."
  26,142,"Tuma nde Saalihu musi…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on ka dammbe (asko) wi'annoo …ìe: Enee, on hulataa Alla, acciron rewugol tanaa Makko sabu kulol Makko?!"
  26,143,"Min, ko mi Nulaa…óo moo…óon, Alla Nulii lam e moo…óon, ko mi hoolaa…óo e nder ko mi yottinanta Mo kon, mi …ìeydataa e dow mu'un mi uytataa …óum kadi."
  26,144,"Huliree Alla …óoftagol Yamiraa…ói Makko …óin e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, …óoftee lam e ko mi yamiri on kon, e ko mi ha…ói on kon e muu…óum."
  26,145,"Mi …óa…ì…ìiraali on njo…ìdi fii ko mi yottinanta Joomi am kon e moo…óon, njo…ìdi am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Alla Jooma tageefooji …óin wanaa e tanaa Makko."
  26,146,"Enee, on tam∆¥ini nde accete…óon e nder koo ko wonu…óon e muu…óum immorde e mo∆¥∆¥ereeji e neemaaji ko on hoolii…ìe hara on hulaa?!"
  26,147,"E nder gese e can…ói ilooji."
  26,148,"E awruuji e tamarooje dim…óe majje …óen ko newii…óe …ìenndu…óe."
  26,149,"Hi…óon ta∆¥a pelle …óen fii yo on wa…óu cuu…ói ho…óon e majji hara onon ko ≈ãelir…ìe lesugol …ói."
  26,150,"Huliree Alla …óoftagol Yamiraa…ói Makko …óin e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaani Makko …óin, …óoftee lam e ko mi yamiri on kon, e ko mi ha…ói on kon e muu…óum."
  26,151,"Wata on …óowor yamaruyee fantiniroo…ìe …ìen e dow wonkiiji mu'un wa…ó…óitagol geddi …óin."
